        <td><img src="images/space80.gif" width="80" height="10"></td>
        <td colspan="3" width="500" cellpadding="10"><h1
        align="center">Sun Healthcare Group, Inc. </h1>
        <p><b>Sun Healthcare Group, Inc. (NYSE: SHG) provides
        high-quality long-term and subacute healthcare in
        facilities in the United States and the United Kingdom.
        Founded in 1989, the company has expanded dramatically
        and is now the third largest contract rehabilitation
        therapy provider, and one of the largest nursing home
        operators in the United States. Sun's operations
        encompass more than 300 inpatient facilities and nearly
        30,000 beds worldwide. </b></p>
        <p><b>If you, or someone you love, requires the services
        of a long-term care or skilled nursing facility, we at
        Sunrise Healthcare Corporation would like to help. Our
        &quot;</b><a href="pages/sunrise.htm"><b>Skilled Nursing
        Facilities</b></a><b>&quot; section will help you find a
        nursing facility close to your home or with the special
        services you require. </b></p>
        <p><b>For more information about Sun Healthcare Group,
        Inc., read &quot;</b><a href="pages/about.htm"><b>About
        Our Company</b></a><b>&quot; or </b><a
        href="pages/moreinfo.htm"><b>fill out this form</b></a><b>.</b>
        </p>
